public interface MethodUnit
extends MethodElement
A representation of the model object 'Method Unit'. A Method Unit is a special Method Element that shall be maintained in a Method Library as a separate unit of control.

The following features are supported:

  • Authors
  • Change Date
  • Change Description
  • Version
  • Copyright Statement
See Also:
UmaPackage.getMethodUnit()
